      • getIcon

        public static ImageIcon getIcon(String iconName)
        Gets the ImageIcon with the specified name.
        Parameters:
        iconName - The name of the icon to load. This is typically the name of the .gif image file.
        Returns:
        The ImageIcon that corresponds to the specified name. Note that if the icon cannot be loaded then the default icon will be returned.

      • loadIcon

        protected static ImageIcon loadIcon(String iconName)
        Loads and caches an ImageIcon that represents the icon that corresponds to the specified file name.
        Parameters:
        iconName - The icon name.
        Returns:
        The ImageIcon that corresponds to the name specified.
